### Request without API key — expect 401 (when auth enabled)
POST {{baseUrl}}/recipes
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "text": "Simple recipe to test auth"
}

### Request with wrong API key — expect 401
POST {{baseUrl}}/recipes
Content-Type: application/json
X-API-Key: wrong-key-here

{
  "text": "Simple recipe to test auth"
}

### Request with correct API key — expect 202
POST {{baseUrl}}/recipes
Content-Type: application/json
X-API-Key: {{apiKey}}

{
  "text": "Simple recipe to test auth"
}

### Health check without API key — expect 200 (always bypasses auth)
GET {{baseUrl}}/health
